Huanglong Scenic and Historic Interest Area in Songpan County, southwest China's Sichuan Province, is an outstanding natural area with forests, lakes and mountain scenery. The video presents the beauty of four seasons in Huanglong, a fairyland on earth. (The video images are provided by Sun Jiapeng and edited by Liu Haibo) Song of Four Seasons Every season has its unique beauty. The series 'Song of Four Seasons' presents the beauty of spring, summer, autumn and winter in different places, showing the amazing nature in different time. (If you want to contribute and have specific expertise, please contact us at nature@cgtn.com.)